      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "SCENIC SUNDARI (6) finished in the minors last time but only a few starts back broke the clock when winning over 457m at this track, taking a Grade 5 in an excellent 25.27. Has the ability and looks a key chance again. WINNIE RUMBLE (2) had been in great form but missed the frame latest when seventh (26.57) in a Grade 5 at this track. Generally a safe beginner but buried in the ruck from a squeeze draw last time. Worth following up. PROCEEDING (4) looks close to another win after finishing third from Box 2 last time (21.84) at this track. Boasts two wins from three starts out of this box. Can feature again. MORE THAN MERRY (7) cannot be underestimated.",
